listeners.tab

Class TabChangeListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • listeners.tab.TabChangeListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.ChangeListener

    public class TabChangeListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.event.ChangeListener
    Implementation of ChangeListener interface. Used by TabbedPane, it registers when selected tab changes. It then changes enabled actions based on newly selected tab.
    Author:
    Milan Radeta
    See Also:
    ActionsManager
